<% @title=t('c_champion.index.title') %>

<div class = "row">
  <div class= "large-12 columns">
  <h1>Nutrition Champions</h1>
  <p> We are supporting a global network of Nutrition Champions, a group of passionate individuals who are working together to end malnutrition. Our nutrition champions come from a variety of backgrounds; they may have developed an innovative approach to tackling malnutrition which is positively affecting their community, they may be training others in practical solutions to fight malnutrition, they may be working in their community to increase awareness of peopleâ€™s right to food or they might be raising their voice on a global platform. </p>
